text: Lakas means strength, power in Tagalog and may refer to: * Lakas ng Bayan (English: People's Power), a political party in the Philippines * Lakas–CMD, a political party in the Philippines founded in 2009 * Lakas–CMD (1991), a political party in the Philippines founded in 1991 * Demetrio B. Lakas (1925–1999), president of Panama * Lakas Tama, studio album by comedian Vice Ganda ==See also== *Laka (disambiguation) *Lakka (disambiguation)
title: Lakas
